# 🎓 College Management System

A simple and responsive **College Management System** built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. This project is designed to simulate a basic interface for managing student and college-related activities such as course details, student profiles, and announcements.

## 🚀 Project Overview

This College Management System aims to simplify and digitize administrative tasks typically handled manually in colleges. It serves as a frontend prototype and showcases UI design, navigation structure, and interactivity.

## ✨ Features

- 🧑‍🎓 Student registration and profile management
- 📚 Course listing with details
- 📅 Academic calendar and announcements
- 🔍 Search functionality for students/courses
- 🖥️ Responsive design for desktop and mobile views

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML** – Structure of the application
- **CSS** – Styling and layout
- **JavaScript** – Interactivity and basic functionality

